Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 6.17-5.15] rtc: pcf2127: clear minute/second interrupt
Date: Sun, 26 Oct 2025 10:48:58 -0400
Message-ID: <20251026144958.26750-20-sashal@kernel.org>
